Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.73,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Because we're going to be \N on the same side.{Start of copy-paste from episode 2 up-to-date as of August 17th 2021 -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:12.07,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I plan on defeating your boss \N and taking over this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:13.78,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:21.20,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,In order to rid this city of gangs who sell drugs to children, \N I need to become a gangster myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.37,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Are you telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.42,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...you're going to join our organization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:26.92,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.46,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what you're getting into?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.46,Secondary,Giorno,0,0,0,,What a nice view...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Yeah! \N If I'm going to take over this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:38.05,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...I'll have to join the organization that rules it \N and work my way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.76,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.14,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a Gang-Star! {End of copy-paste from episode 2 up-to-date as of August 17th 2021 -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.10,Main,Kid 1,0,0,0,,Pass! Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.16,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.16,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.33,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll report back that I couldn't \N locate Luca's assailant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:05.79,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...then introduce you as a \N prospective member of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:11.30,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,However, if at any point it becomes known \N that you're planning to overthrow the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.26,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...I won't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.38,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Known traitors are beyond help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.89,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You alone will have to atone \N for your transgression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:29.48,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,That aside, I'm willing to gamble  \Non your golden dream... {I hate this line so much.... -Axel}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:33.44,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...and the noble resolve you showed me \N by ripping your own arm off, Giorno Giovanna.
